ion.png" decoding=3D"async" width=3D"500" height=3D"375" class=3D"mw-file-e=
lement" data-file-width=3D"784" data-file-height=3D"588"></a><figcaption>Gr=
aphic showing relationships between radioactivity and detected ionizing rad=
